.Dd 2015-10-08
.Dt WC 1
.Os sbase
.Sh NAME
.Nm wc
.Nd word count
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl c | Fl m
.Op Fl lw
.Op Ar file ...
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
writes the number of lines, words and bytes in each
.Ar file
to stdout.
If no
.Ar file
is given
.Nm
reads from stdin.
.Sh OPTIONS
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl c | Fl l | Fl m | Fl w
Print the number of bytes | lines | characters | words.
.El
.Sh STANDARDS
The
.Nm
utility is compliant with the
.St -p1003.1-2013
specification.
